<title>Jarqyrap ketti aınala РӘЖ162</title>
<key>Cm</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.       Cm                   Bb
 Jarqyrap ketti aınala, nurǵa bólep aımaqty,
.  Cm                     Bb
 Demalǵan malshylarǵa, top perishte ún qatty:
.  Fm                    G
 Top perishte ún qatty, ún qatty.
.   Cm                       Bb
 Betlehemge bet buryńdar, besik jyry toılansyn!
.  Cm                      Bb
 Qutqarýshy keldi álemge, barlyq adam oılansyn.
.  Fm                    G
 Barlyq adam oılansyn, oılansyn.

[C1]
.   Fm        Bb
   Qýanyp shattanyńdar!
.    Eb          Cm
   Másih keldi dúnıege,
.    Fm            Bb
   Qarsy alyńdar adamzat,
.    Eb            Cm
   Barshaǵa jar salyńdar.
.     Fm      Bb
   Qýanyp shattanyńdar,
.      Eb            Cm
   Tańǵajaıyp kúıge enip,
.    Fm          G           Cm
   Ǵajapqa tamsanyńdar, tamsanyńdar.

[V2]
 Qundaqtaýly bala jatyr,
 Mal baılaǵan aqyrda,
 Nur beıneli pana jatyr,
 Halqy kútken ǵasyrlar.
 Halqy kútken ǵasyrlar, ǵasyrlar.
 Malshylardan elge habar,
 Osylaısha taraldy,
 Kıeli Rýh kóleńkesi bizge pana bere aldy,
 Bizge pana bere aldy, bere aldy.

[C2]
   Qýanyp shattanyńdar!
   Másih keldi dúnıege,
   Qarsy alyńdar adamzat,
   Barshaǵa jar salyńdar.
   Qýanyp shattanyńdar,
   Tańǵajaıyp kúıge enip,
   Ǵajapqa tamsanyńdar, án salyńdar.
   Án salyńdar Iemizge, án salyńdar.</lyrics>
</song>